HTML-Feature version 1.0.2
==========================

This module extracts some feature sentence from HTML.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    LWP::Simple
    Encode
    Encode::Guess
    HTML::TreeBuilder
    Statistics::Lite

